videos.description: Oklahoma's Jamal Bieniemy steals the ball and finds Brady Manek at the other end for the monster slam as Oklahoma leads 30-18.
videos.headline: Manek slams it home off the steal

videos.description: Miles Reynolds takes the fast-break pass from Kristian Doolittle and banks it in high off the backboard.
videos.headline: Reynolds banks in transition layup high off the glass
